      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver that won't break the bank? Here's a great opportunity! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives well, handling your everyday commuting needs with ease. You'll notice some cosmetic wear consistent with its age, and there may be a minor issue or two, but nothing that keeps it off the road. It's been honestly priced to reflect its condition, making it a smart pick for a budget-conscious buyer who wants dependable transportation without paying for perfection. Come take it for a spin \u2014 you might be pleasantly surprised!",
