    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Honest Deal \u2013 A Budget-Friendly Ride That Gets You Moving! \ud83d\ude97\n\nLooking for an affordable car that handles daily commutes without a hefty price tag? This one could be your answer! This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but does show its age with some visible wear and minor imperfections you'd expect from a well-used car. It's not perfect, but it's priced to reflect that honestly. Great for a buyer who needs reliable transportation and wants to keep costs low. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you \u2014 no surprises here, just straightforward value! \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 20000.0,
