      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a fair-condition car that offers reliable transportation with some cosmetic and mechanical considerations. The exterior shows visible wear including minor dents, some paint fading, and light surface rust in a few spots \u2014 nothing catastrophic, but noticeable up close. The interior is functional but shows its age with worn upholstery, some scuffs on the trim, and general signs of regular use. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term \u2014 expect to budget for items like tires, brakes, or minor repairs depending on your inspection findings. This is a solid choice for a buyer who wants a usable vehicle at a fair price and doesn't mind putting in a little work to bring it up to their standards. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged, and we welcome any questions about the car's history.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we believe in being completely transparent with prospective buyers about what that entails. The exterior shows considerable wear, including multiple dents, scratches, and areas of paint deterioration or fading that are clearly visible. The interior has seen better days as well, with worn upholstery, cracked or damaged trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 buyers should budget for repairs and factor that into their purchasing decision. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer who simply needs basic transportation and understands what they're getting. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we've priced it accordingly to reflect the vehicle's current state honestly.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and represents a solid, dependable used car purchase. The exterior presents well overall \u2014 paint retains a good shine with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use; there are no significant dents or structural damage. The interior is clean and well-maintained, with moderate wear on the driver's seat and some light scuffing on high-contact surfaces, but no tears, major stains, or broken components. Mechanically, this car runs reliably \u2014 the engine starts smoothly, transmission shifts cleanly, and brakes respond well. All major systems including AC, heat, windows, and lights are fully functional. Tires have good tread remaining. This is not a mint-condition showroom vehicle, but it is genuinely road-ready and trustworthy for everyday driving. Maintenance has been kept up, and there are no known mechanical issues. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
